148
00:09:31,703 --> 00:09:35,696
On the upside, it does bode well for Dad
getting a "yes" when he proposes.

149
00:09:37,125 --> 00:09:39,275
He has a right to know about this.

150
00:09:39,544 --> 00:09:42,661
