175
00:11:14,222 --> 00:11:16,417
Mrs Kranz upstairs...

176
00:11:18,226 --> 00:11:21,377
- How about you, Dad?
- Sure, I know some people.

177
00:11:21,688 --> 00:11:23,280
Really, you do?

178
00:11:23,523 --> 00:11:25,081
- I think.
- You think?

179
00:11:25,317 --> 00:11:27,911
Maybe I do, maybe I don't.
I hate this shirt.

180
00:11:28,195 --> 00:11:30,186
I've got to change this shirt.

181
00:11:32,449 --> 00:11:36,237
- That was fruitless.
- I'll tell you one thing I'm sure of.

182
00:11:37,663 --> 00:11:39,381
Yes?

183
00:11:39,623 --> 00:11:42,183
Oh, I'm allowed to talk now, am l?

