and I bet he'll pop the question.

186
00:11:51,635 --> 00:11:54,672
- We have to tell him.
- But we don't know what he knows.

187
00:11:54,972 --> 00:11:57,406
If she'd told him
she'd been married six times,

188
00:11:57,683 --> 00:12:00,641
- he would remember.
