189
00:12:00,936 --> 00:12:04,008
Maybe this shirt isn't so bad
with this new jacket.

190
00:12:04,314 --> 00:12:06,748
- What do you think ofthis jacket?
- It's nice.

191
00:12:07,025 --> 00:12:09,778
Sherry's been married six times?

192
00:12:10,070 --> 00:12:13,346
- Who told you that?
- They did.

193
00:12:18,954 --> 00:12:20,945
