194
00:12:21,206 --> 00:12:24,801
I'd love to see the first shirt
with the second jacket.

195
00:12:25,127 --> 00:12:28,517
You got this from the investigator.
You did hire him.

196
00:12:28,839 --> 00:12:33,037
I guess there's no use in denying it.
Yes, we did hire him.

197
00:12:33,385 --> 00:12:36,775
Although the word "we"
is not entirely accurate.

198
00:12:37,097 --> 00:12:40,134
- Frasier, I am shocked that...
- Shut up, Niles.

